text: Takiéta is a town in south central Niger, in Mirriah Department, Zinder Region.Takieta, Niger Page. Falling Rain Genomics, Inc. 1996-2004 It lies along the Route Nationale 1 (Niger), the nation's primary east-west highway, roughly halfway between Zinder and Tessaoua. ==References== Category:Populated places in Niger Category:Zinder Region
